And we are back!😎
Here are the quick details to get you started. 

1. In the upcoming 5 days, we will be sharing a color of the day everyday on our feed. So make sure you switch your post notifications on.

3. Once done, drop a comment on the same post, so we can check it out and tag your friends to participate.
